data.description: Well cared for 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home in Olentangy School District. Near Highbanks Park. North of Powell Road between Route 23 & State Route 315. Formal Living Room, Dining Room, Eat In Kitchen, and Family Room on First Floor, as well as 3 Season Room. Hardwood floors on first floor. Deck with Swing and Fire Pit. Upstairs has three bedrooms and Owners Suite. Finished Basement has been waterproofed. 2021 Roof & Furnace. 2022 Basement Waterproofing & Kitchen Renovation with Granite Counters. Radon Mitigation System in place. Optional HOA $25 year.
